name: gcc_impl_linux-aarch64
raw_recipe:
# This file created by conda-build 3.21.4
# ------------------------------------------------

package:
  name: gcc_impl_linux-aarch64
  version: 11.1.0
source:
  - patches:
      - patches/0021-Hardcode-HAVE_ALIGNED_ALLOC-1-in-libstdc-v3-configur.patch
    url: https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/gcc/gcc-11.1.0/gcc-11.1.0.tar.gz
build:
  binary_relocation:
    - bin/*
    - lib/*.so*
    - libexec/**/*.so*
    - libexec/**/cc1*
    - libexec/**/collect2
    - libexec/**/gcc
    - libexec/**/lto*
    - libexec/**/plugin/gengtype
  detect_binary_files_with_prefix: false
  ignore_run_exports:
    - __glibc
  missing_dso_whitelist:
    - '*'
  number: 5
  runpath_whitelist:
    - x86_64-conda-linux-gnu/sysroot/lib/libpthread-2.12.2.so
  string: hce514e5_5
requirements:
  build:
    - binutils_impl_linux-aarch64 2.36.1 he24a65f_2
    - binutils_impl_linux-ppc64le 2.36.1 h17f093b_2
    - gcc_bootstrap_linux-64 9.3.0 hbd0e1d1_33
    - gcc_impl_linux-ppc64le 11.1.0 h0f544c2_4
    - gfortran_impl_linux-aarch64 11.1.0.*
    - gxx_impl_linux-aarch64 11.1.0.*
    - gxx_impl_linux-ppc64le 11.1.0 h0f544c2_4
    - kernel-headers_linux-aarch64 4.18.0 h5b4a56d_12
    - kernel-headers_linux-ppc64le 3.10.0 h23d7e6c_12
    - ld_impl_linux-aarch64 2.36.1 h4e2ea54_2
    - ld_impl_linux-ppc64le 2.36.1 h8031a8f_2
    - libgcc-devel_linux-ppc64le 11.1.0 h01978d2_4
    - libstdcxx-devel_linux-ppc64le 11.1.0 h01978d2_4
    - sysroot_linux-aarch64 2.17 h43d7e78_12
    - sysroot_linux-ppc64le 2.17 h395ec9b_12
  host:
    - kernel-headers_linux-aarch64 4.18.0 h5b4a56d_12
    - sysroot_linux-aarch64 2.17 h43d7e78_12
  run:
    - binutils_impl_linux-aarch64 2.36.1.*
    - libgcc-devel_linux-aarch64 11.1.0 h868b92f_5
    - sysroot_linux-aarch64
test:
  commands:
    - echo conda_cos7
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/aarch64-conda_cos7-linux-gnu-gcc
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/aarch64-conda_cos7-linux-gnu-cpp
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu-gcc
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu-cpp
    - test ! -f ${PREFIX}/bin/gcc
    - test ! -f ${PREFIX}/bin/cpp
    - CC=$(${PREFIX}/bin/*-gcc -dumpmachine)-gcc
    - ${CC} -Wall tests/aligned_alloc.c -c -o c_aligned.o -v
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu/lib/libgcc_s.so
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/aarch64-conda-linux-gnu/lib/libgomp.spec
  files:
    - tests
  requires:
    - sysroot_linux-aarch64 2.17.*
about:
  home: https://gcc.gnu.org/
  license: GPL-3.0-only WITH GCC-exception-3.1
  summary: GNU C Compiler
extra:
  copy_test_source_files: true
  final: true
  recipe-maintainers:
    - beckermr
    - isuruf
